{
  "chapter": 10,
  "chapter_summary": "陆小凤与小玉乘小艇逃亡，小艇被宫主（牛肉汤）在船底凿了两个洞用蜡封住，海水浸泡后蜡溶船沉。小玉早有准备，用黄蜡堵洞保住了小艇。两人靠岸后，陆小凤带小玉回到海边小草棚，发现沙曼藏身于弥勒佛像中。沙曼谎称成亲之事，实为说谎，两人重逢相爱。小玉识趣离开后，陆小凤与沙曼在草棚中相拥。此时牛肉汤突然出现，冷嘲热讽，并告知宫九将在半个时辰内追来，岛上虽有五千七百多处可藏身之处，但宫九武功高强，三人难逃。牛肉汤以沙曼曾与宫九有过来往刺激陆小凤，又打赌三个时辰内宫九必能找到他们。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你果然不会说谎，我不喜欢你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你以为我真的怕你喜欢我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你不怕？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我告诉你这些事，只不过因为我本来就不会说谎而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "不管你为什么说了老实话，现在你可以穿好衣裳了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我反正已被你看过了，为什么还要穿好衣裳？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你千万不能这么做！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "因为……因为我是个色狼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我不怕色狼，难道色狼反而怕我了？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "色狼也不怕，色狼只不过怕他自己会……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你会不会游水？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "这下子真的完了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "什么事完了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你那位宫主不但要杀我，还要将你也一起杀了灭口。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你知道？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "她在这小船底下打了两个洞，用蜡封住，被海水一泡，蜡就会溶，海水涌进来，这条船就要沉了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你既然早就知道，为什么还要坐这条船？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为我早就想尝尝被淹死是什么滋味的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我知道你心里一定在骂我是个小混蛋，其实，你若不遇见我，也一样是会被淹死的，现在多了个人陪你，有什么不好？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "我只不过有点后悔。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "后悔什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "后悔刚才没有真的喜欢你。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你笑什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这块蜡溶开怎么办？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "我不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我知道，这样的蜡我已准备了十七八块。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "原来你不是小混蛋，却是条小狐狸。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我虽然很想尝尝被淹死的滋味，可是还没有被人真的喜欢过就糊里糊涂的死了，岂非有点冤枉？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你那位宫主看到你活生生的回去了，不知道会不会被吓死？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "她不会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你怎么知道不会？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为她每次要我做事，总是想把我也一起杀了灭口，只可惜每次我都没有死，每次她看到我活着回去，反而好像很高兴，因为她知道我以后又可以替她做事了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你既然知道她要害你，为什么还要替她做事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为我若不做，就真的要死了，死得很快。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你是个好人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你眼光总算不错；",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你这两条像眉毛一样的胡子，虽然有点讨厌，可是你这人倒不算难看。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "等你再长大一点，你说不定就会喜欢我这胡子了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "只可惜你是陆小凤。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "这又有什么可惜？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你若不是陆小凤，我就一定会嫁给你，就算做小老婆都没关系。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "我是陆小凤，你为什么不能嫁给我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为我不想做寡妇。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "嫁给陆小凤就会做寡妇？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我那位宫主一心想要你的命，九少爷也未必喜欢你活下去，我若嫁给你，也许不出三天就要做寡妇了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "做寡妇好像也是很好玩的事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "不好玩，一点也不好玩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "好玩，一定很好玩。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "女人迟早都要嫁人的，嫁了人就有丈夫，寡妇却没有，一个人自由自在的，也没有人管，还可以去偷别人的丈夫，岂非好玩得很？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你为什么不说话，是不是觉得我说得很有道理？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "原来你不仅是小狐狸，你还是小混蛋。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "只不过你尽管放心，我这小混蛋，还不想嫁给你这大混蛋。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我要回去了，你呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你究竟回不回去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "我有栋很漂亮的房子，就在这附近，你想不想去看看？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你说谎，我可不喜欢会说谎的男人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "我那间屋里还有个朋友在等着我，他肚子大大的，不但好玩极了，而且他从来不说谎话。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "原来你不但会说谎，还会吹牛。世界上什么样的人都有，从来不说谎的人我倒还没有见过。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你若不信，为什么不自己去看看？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "去就去，有什么了不起，反正……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "反正我又不怕你，是你怕我。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这就是你的漂亮房子？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "这房子又凉快，又通风，你说有哪点不好？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "好……好……好不要脸。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这就是你的朋友？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你看他会不会说谎？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我也没有说谎。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好朋友，我就知道你一定还在这里等着我，你非但不会说谎，也不会出卖朋友。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "可是我会咬人。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我不但会咬人，还会说谎。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "你怎么会到这里来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你能到我的家去，我为什么不能到你的家来？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "你当然能来，随时都能来，可是……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "今天你却不该来的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "今天岂非是你成亲的日子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我刚才岂非已告诉过你，我不但会咬人，还会说谎。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "现在我才明白了，为什么你喜欢会说谎的女孩子，因为你喜欢曼姑娘。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "现在你们可以真的彼此喜欢喜欢，我却得走了，再不走只怕就要被你赶出去了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "真的彼此喜欢喜欢，这句话是什么意思？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "就是这个意思。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "好，好极了，你们的武功如果有你们刚才的动作一半好，一定没有人能受得了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "你好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我不好。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "这倒是实话，你这人的确不太好。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我只要你凭良心说一句话。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "说什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "做这种事，究竟是我好，还是她好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "你们不能比。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "因为做这种事的方法有两种。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "哪两种？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "一种是人，一种是野兽。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "人死了之后呢？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "我记得有人说过，一万个死人，也比不上一条活母狗。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这一定是个聪明人说的话了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "你是人，还是母狗，也许我还不太清楚，我只知道一件事。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你知道什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "知道我们还活着，至少现在还活着。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "还能活多久？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "只要能活一天，也比你活一万年好。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你错了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "哦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "也许你们还能活一天半。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "哦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这是个很大的海岛。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "哦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "据我们估计，这岛上至少有五千七百多个可以躲藏的地方。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "哦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "只要你们能躲过十八个时辰，也许就可以活到一百八十岁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "只可惜你们一定躲不过的。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为你们就算是两只蚂蚁，他也可以在半个时辰中把你们找出来捏死。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "是你？还是他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "他就是你的九哥？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "当然是。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "他甚至还愿意先让你们半个时辰。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "怎么让？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "从现在开始，这半个时辰里他绝不追你们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "绝不？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "他说的话，每个字都像钉在墙里，一个钉子一个眼。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "这点我倒相信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "就算你不信，睡在你旁边的人至少应该相信。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
